{"type":"message","id":"664b914e","parentId":"3b00c178","timestamp":"2026-06-10T02:55:44.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No Unity process running, good. Let me check if there's a hot update pipeline running via command line args.\n\nActually, the `Get-Process -Name \"Unity\"` returned exit code 1 which means no Unity processes found. So no existing pipeline running.\n\nNow let me drop the sub-agent to handle the actual work. The sub-agent will:\n1. Kill any Unity Editor processes (already confirmed none, but do it anyway)\n2. Git pull all submodules\n3. Run the batch file\n4. Check results\n5. Notify accordingly\n\nLet me spawn the sub-agent with the full task.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没有 Unity 进程在跑。我开个子 session 来跑热更流水线。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_KqrWHZQvSrerYg5CzB5R1179","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"执行更新测试服（客户端热更）流水线\n\n步骤如下：\n1. 关掉所有 Unity Editor 进程（kill Unity.exe）\n2. 用 git 命令手动更新主工程所有子模块：\n   - cd E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon && git pull\n   - 遍历子模块（git submodule foreach），检查 detached HEAD 状态\n   - 对 detached HEAD 的子模块，根据 .gitmodules 或 git submodule status 显示的分支名执行 git checkout <branch> 再 git pull\n   - 确保所有子模块指向正确分支的最新提交\n3. 运行 Unity 热更流水线：E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\n4. 检查编译结果：\n   - 记录日志文件的 LastWriteTime，执行后检查是否更新\n   - 扫描 BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log 检查错误（error CS\\d+|git更新失败|Build completed with.*errors）\n5. 通知：\n   - ✅ 成功 → 用 node scripts/feishu_send_group.mjs oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 hotupdate-ok 在开发群 @兵王\n   - ❌ 失败 → 通过飞书私聊通知主人（sessions_send）\n6. 每一步状态变化都要通过飞书消息及时反馈","mode":"run","context":"isolated"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":58,"output":529,"cacheRead":20224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20811,"cost":{"input":0.00000812,"output":0.00014812,"cacheRead":0.0005662719999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0007225119999999999}},"sto