{"type":"message","id":"bfb326f5","parentId":"2d9a93a3","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:44:02.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Java is installed and working. The exit code 1 is just because PowerShell treats stderr as error stream, but the output is correct. Now I need to:\n\n1. Add the JDK bin directory to the system PATH\n2. Create a directory for apktool (e.g., C:\\tools\\apktool)\n3. Download apktool.jar and the wrapper script\n4. Add that directory to PATH\n\nLet me do all of this.\n\nFirst, let me add Java to system PATH.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Java 正常工作。现在配置环境变量并下载 apktool。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_itFZqb9U73tbLmapRxBp0331","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Add Java to system PATH for current and future sessions\n$javaBin = \"C:\\Program Files\\Eclipse Adoptium\\jdk-17.0.19.10-hotspot\\bin\"\n\n# Add to current session PATH\n$env:Path = \"$javaBin;$env:Path\"\n\n# Set JAVA_HOME\n$env:JAVA_HOME = \"C:\\Program Files\\Eclipse Adoptium\\jdk-17.0.19.10-hotspot\"\n\n# Persist to machine PATH\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"JAVA_HOME\", $env:JAVA_HOME, \"Machine\")\n$currentPath = [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"Machine\")\nif ($currentPath -notlike \"*$javaBin*\") {\n    [Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"$javaBin;$currentPath\", \"Machine\")\n}\n\n# Create apktool directory\n$apktoolDir = \"C:\\tools\\apktool\"\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $apktoolDir -Force | Out-Null\n\n# Add apktool dir to PATH\n$env:Path = \"$apktoolDir;$env:Path\"\n$currentPath = [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"Machine\")\nif ($currentPath -notlike \"*$apktoolDir*\") {\n    [Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"$apktoolDir;$currentPath\", \"Machine\")\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"Java PATH and JAVA_HOME configured\"\nWrite-Host \"Java test:\"\njava -version 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":274,"output":513,"cacheRead":28800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29587,"cost":{"input":0.000038360000000000005,"output":0.00014364,"cacheRead":0.0008064,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0009884}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781088237899,"responseId":"c293ad94-fa93-40c6-a0dc-30fb101291ca"}}
