{"type":"message","id":"502f1f84","parentId":"2e84c289","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:44:45.772Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me download apktool. I need:\n1. apktool.jar (the latest version)\n2. apktool.bat (Windows wrapper script)\n\nLatest apktool can be found at:\n- apktool.jar: https://github.com/iBotPeaches/Apktool/releases/latest\n- Windows wrapper: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iBotPeaches/Apktool/master/scripts/windows/apktool.bat\n\nLet me first find the latest version.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在下载 apktool。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_eK7oh1o5Gim96fHVUyLu9620","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Get latest apktool release info\n$releases = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://api.github.com/repos/iBotPeaches/Apktool/releases/latest\"\n$tag = $releases.tag_name\nWrite-Host \"Latest version: $tag\"\n\n# Download apktool.jar\n$jarUrl = \"https://github.com/iBotPeaches/Apktool/releases/download/$tag/apktool_$($tag.Replace('v','')).jar\"\n$apktoolDir = \"C:\\tools\\apktool\"\nWrite-Host \"Downloading from: $jarUrl\"\nInvoke-WebRequest -Uri $jarUrl -OutFile \"$apktoolDir\\apktool.jar\" -UseBasicParsing\nWrite-Host \"apktool.jar downloaded\"\n\n# Download the Windows wrapper script\n$batUrl = \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iBotPeaches/Apktool/refs/heads/master/scripts/windows/apktool.bat\"\nInvoke-WebRequest -Uri $batUrl -OutFile \"$apktoolDir\\apktool.bat\" -UseBasicParsing\nWrite-Host \"apktool.bat downloaded\"\n\n# Add apktool dir to User PATH\n$userPath = [Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"User\")\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable(\"Path\", \"$apktoolDir;$userPath\", \"User\")\nWrite-Host \"apktool added to PATH\"\n\n# Set current session path\n$env:Path = \"$apktoolDir;$env:Path\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":55,"output":501,"cacheRead":30720,"cacheWrite