{"type":"message","id":"c43fc115","parentId":"a4c13ad7","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:54:11.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Most of these hits are garbage - they're partial matches from binary data. The only real URLs I see are:\n- `https://android.googlesource.com/toolchain/llvm-project` - This is a toolchain reference, not app-specific\n\nThe actual game server URLs are likely encrypted/obfuscated or stored differently in IL2CPP. Let me check the global-metadata.dat which might contain the managed string table.\n\nActually, let me look at the FGUI XML files which might contain login UI text and clues about the login flow.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_eZC51hF5mUDYVK837AEG7152","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Search FGUI for login-related UI text\nSelect-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\assets\\FGUI\\ChineseSimplified.xml\" -Pattern \"登录|login|Login|账号|密码|账户|手机|验证\" | Select-Object -First 20\n\nWrite-Host \"=== I18N CSV for login ===\"\nSelect-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\assets\\I18N\\I18N.csv\" -Pattern \"登录|login|Login|LOGIN|账号|password|Password|account\" | Select-Object -First 20","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":272,"output":317,"cacheRead":77312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77901,"cost":{"input":0.00003808,"output":0.00008876000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002164736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002291576}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781088848099,"responseId":"d43eb6fd-f38c-4a7a-a680-29e3b7a6d465"}}
