:".class Lcom/foxwq/yhwq/wechat/WechatLogin$1;\r\n.super Landroid/os/AsyncTask;\r\n.source \"WechatLogin.java\"\r\n\r\n\r\n# annotations\r\n.annotation system Ldalvik/annotation/EnclosingMethod;\r\n    value = Lcom/foxwq/yhwq/wechat/WechatLogin;->SendGet(Ljava/lang/String;Ljava/lang/String;I)V\r\n.end annotation\r\n\r\n.annotation system Ldalvik/annotation/InnerClass;\r\n    accessFlags = 0x0\r\n    name = null\r\n.end annotation\r\n\r\n.annotation system Ldalvik/annotation/Signature;\r\n    value = {\r\n        \"Landroid/os/AsyncTask<\",\r\n        \"Ljava/lang/Object;\",\r\n        \"Ljava/lang/Object;\",\r\n        \"Ljava/lang/String;\",\r\n        \">;\"\r\n    }\r\n.end annotation\r\n\r\n\r\n# instance fields\r\n.field final synthetic val$param:Ljava/lang/String;\r\n\r\n.field final synthetic val$type:I\r\n\r\n.field final synthetic val$url:Ljava/lang/String;\r\n\r\n\r\n# direct methods\r\n.method constructor <init>(Ljava/lang/String;Ljava/lang/String;I)V\r\n    .locals 0\r\n\r\n    .line 79\r\n    iput-object p1, p0, Lcom/foxwq/yhwq/wechat/WechatLogin$1;->val$url:Ljava/lang/String;\r\n\r\n    iput-object p2, p0, Lcom/foxwq/yhwq/wechat/WechatLogin$1;->val$param:Ljava/lang/String;\r\n\r\n    iput p3, p0, Lcom/foxwq/yhwq/wechat/WechatLogin$1;->val$type:I\r\n\r\n    invoke-direct {p0}, Landroid/os/AsyncTask;-><init>()V\r\n\r\n    return-void\r\n.end method\r\n\r\n\r\n# virtual methods\r\n.method protected bridge synthetic doInBackground([Ljava/lang/Object;)Ljava/lang/Object;\r\n    .locals 0\r\n\r\n    .line 79\r\n    invoke-virtual {p0, p1}, Lcom/foxwq/yhwq/wechat/WechatLogin$1;->doInBackground([Ljava/lang/Object;)Ljava/lang/String;\r\n\r\n    move-result-object p1","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781088863260}}
{"type":"message","id":"41e42600","parentId":"879a0f68","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:54:41.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I now have a good understanding of the login flow. Let me compile my findings and deliver a comprehensive analysis to the user.\n\nSummary of what I've found:\n\n**App Info:**\n- Package: `com.foxwq.yhwq` (野狐围棋/野狐围棋)\n- Unity IL2CPP + Android native bridge\n- Main Activity: `com.foxwq.yhwq.MainActivity` (extends UnityPlayerActivity)\n\n**Login Methods (3 third-party + built-in):**\n\n1. **微信登录 (WeChat Login)**:\n   - WeChat App ID: `wxd506e81fe975a813`\n   - WeChat App Secret: `e9d5f2b83335c1dbca8b37392ee482cf`\n   - Flow: Open WeChat → Get Auth Code → Call WeChat API `/sns/oauth2/access_token` (client-side!) → Get user info via `/sns/userinfo` → Send results to Unity via `UnitySendMessage(\"GameManager\", \"WXLoginCallback\", \"0;{code}\")` → Unity calls game backend\n   - **Security concern**: The WeChat App Secret is hardcoded in the APK! This is a serious vulnerability as anyone can extract it.\n\n2. **QQ登录**:\n   - QQ App ID: `1112222490`\n   - Uses Tencent SDK `com.tencent.tauth.Tencent`\n   - Flow: Login → GetUserInfo → Send to Unity via callback\n\n3. **谷歌登录 (Google Login)**:\n   - Google Client ID: `709524256366-9mqf22e07votdi1v6up1pjlsiji2o13e.apps.googleusercontent.com`\n\n4. **手机号/验证码登录 (Phone Login)**:\n   - Bind phone number UI exists (BindingPhone.xml)\n   - Password reset flow exists\n   - One-tap login (自动一键登录)\n\n5. **游客登录**: Available\n\n**Game Backend Communication:**\n- Unity GameObject: `GameManager`\n- Callbacks: `WXLoginCallback`, `QQLoginCallback`, `GoogleLoginCallback`, `WXGetOpenIdCallback`\n- The actual game server API calls happen in the Unity C# code (compiled into libil2cpp.so, encrypted/obfuscated)\n\n**Key Security Issues Found:**\n1. ❌ **WeChat App Secret hardcoded** in Constants.java → `e9d5f2b83335c1dbca8b37392ee482cf`\n2. ❌ **Server-side access_token exchange done client-side** → The app sends its AppID+Secret directly to WeChat API from the Android app\n3. ❌ **UnitySendMessage callbacks are not authenticated** → Any code could potentially send fake login callbacks\n\nThe actual game backend API endpoints are in the Unity IL2CPP binary (libil2cpp.so) which is 81MB and would need more sophisticated tools (like il2cppDumper + IDA Pro/Ghidra) to fully reverse engineer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"分析结果如下。\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 野狐围棋登录功能逆向分析\n\n### 应用概览\n\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 包名 | `com.foxwq.yhwq` |\n| 框架 | Unity (IL2CPP) + Android Native Bridge |\n| 入口 | `com.foxwq.yhwq.MainActivity` (继承 UnityPlayerActivity) |\n| Unity 组件 | `GameManager` — 接收所有登录回调 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔐 登录方式一览\n\n#### 1️⃣ 微信登录（OAuth + 客户端凭据泄露）\n\n流程：\n```\nUnity → Java: OpenWechatLogin()\n  → 调起微信 SDK (snsapi_userinfo)\n    → 微信返回 auth code\n      → WXEntryActivity.onSendAuthResp()\n        → UnitySendMessage(\"GameManager\", \"WXLoginCallback\", \"0;{code}\")\n          → Unity C# 用 code 调用游戏后端 API 登录\n```\n\n**⚠️ 关键漏洞：** WeChat App Secret 硬编码在 APK 中\n\n```java\n// Constants.java\nWX_APP_ID     = \"wxd506e81fe975a813\"\nWX_APP_SECRET = \"e9d5f2…82cf\"\n```\n\n而且客户端直接拿 Secret 调微信 API：\n```\nhttps://api.weixin.qq.com/sns/oauth2/access_token?appid=wxd506e81fe975a813\n  &secret=e9d5f2…82cf\n  &code={code}&grant_type=authorization_code\n```\n\n这意味着 **任何人都可以提取你的 WX_APP_SECRET**，用来伪造 access_token 请求。\n\n#### 2️⃣ QQ 登录\n\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| QQ App ID | `1112222490` |\n| 回调名 | `QQLoginCallback` |\n| 逻辑 | `Tencent.login()` → `getUserInfo()` → 回调 Unity |\n\n#### 3️⃣ 谷歌登录\n\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 谷歌 Client ID | `709524256366-9mqf22e07votdi1v6up1pjlsiji2o13e.apps.googleusercontent.com` |\n| 回调名 | `GoogleLoginCallback` |\n\n#### 4️⃣ 手机号 + 密码登录\n\nFGUI 资源文件显示存在以下 UI 组件和流程：\n- `IOSLogin/BindingPhone.xml` — 绑定手机界面\n- 手机号输入 + 验证码输入 + 密码输入\n- `保存并登录` 按钮\n- `修改登录密码`\n- 一键登录（场景授权）\n- 游客登录\n\n#### 5️⃣ 游客登录\n\n零门槛，但有风险提示：\n> \"更换设备或卸载App账号将会丢失\"\n\n---\n\n### 🔄 登录数据流\n\n```\n┌──────────────┐    OAuth Token     ┌──────────────┐\n│  微信/QQ/谷歌  │ ←──────────────→  │  Java Bridge  │\n│    SDK        │                   │  MainActivity │\n└──────────────┘                    └──────┬───────┘\n                                          │ UnitySendMessage()\n                                          │ (\"GameManager\", \"WXLoginCallback\", ...)\n                                          ▼\n                                   ┌──────────────┐\n                                   │  Unity C#     │  ← 核心业务逻辑在 IL2CPP 中\n                                   │  GameManager  │      libil2cpp.so (81MB)\n                                   └──────┬───────┘\n                                          │ HTTP(s)\n                                          ▼\n                                   ┌──────────────┐\n                                   │  野狐游戏后端  │\n                                   │  (未知 URL)   │\n                                   └──────────────┘\n```\n\n游戏后端 API 地址在 Unity C# 代码中（IL2CPP 编译后为原生 SO 文件），需要用 il2cppDumper + Ghidra / IDA Pro 才能进一步提取。\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ 已发现的安全问题\n\n| 问题 | 严重程度 | 详情 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| **WeChat App Secret 硬编码** | 🔴 高危 | `e9d5f2b83335c1dbca8b37392ee482cf` 明文在 APK 中，任何人可提取 |\n| **客户端直调微信 Token API** | 🟡 中危 | App Secret 在客户端发起 HTTP 请求，可被中间人窃取 |\n| **UnitySendMessage 无校验** | 🟡 中危 | 登录回调通过 Java → Unity 字符串传递，理论上可被 hook/伪造 |\n| **微信 auth code 网络回调明文** | 🟡 中危 | `WXGetOpenIdCallback` 回调数据可能被截获 |\n\n---\n\n需要进一步用 il2cppDumper 提取游戏后端 API 地址吗？或者你想重点关注某个登录方式做自动化？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":624,"output":1761,"cacheRead":89984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92369,"cost":{"input":0.00008736,"output":0.00049308,"cacheRead":0.002519552,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003099992}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781088863263,"responseId":"5a1d2077-5ccf-4060-a88b-4d3097c92182"}}
