{"type":"message","id":"d0ecb9dc","parentId":"dc41a70f","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:58:17.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"App ID is `wx09786c3fb9eac9a4`. Now let me look at the existing app.js, settings page, and any auth-related code.\n\nFor the WeChat Mini Program, I need to implement:\n\n1. **wx.login()** to get the code\n2. Send the code to a backend server to exchange for session/token\n3. Use the server's WeChat API (with the AppID+AppSecret from the APK) to get openid/session_key\n4. Store the login state\n\nBut wait - the user wants to use the \"相关信息\" from the APK analysis to do WeChat login. The key info from the APK was:\n- WX_APP_ID: `wxd506e81fe975a813`\n- WX_APP_SECRET: `e9d5f…2cf`\n\nHowever, this is the WeChat Open Platform App ID from the 野狐围棋 app, NOT the user's personal WeChat Mini Program. For a WeChat Mini Program, you use `wx.login()` to get a code, then use the Mini Program's own appid+secret (from WeChat Official Account Platform) to call the backend API.\n\nThe user's Mini Program has appid `wx09786c3fb9eac9a4` which is different.\n\nI think what the user means is: they want to use the WeChat login flow in their Mini Program to authenticate users. The Mini Program's built-in `wx.login()` + server-side `code2Session` API is the way to do it.\n\nLet me look at what pages exist and understand the current state of the project better.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2MVXADbkqfI84RmUF39G7873","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\miniprogram\\app.js\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1289,"output":451,"cacheRead":85760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87500,"cost":{"input":0.00018046000000000002,"output":0.00012628000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00240128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0027080200000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781089091433,"responseId":"f7cf8017-0545-4350-8797-a02fd0bb2d1c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f707106f","parentId":"d0ecb9dc","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:58:17.950Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_2MVXADbkqfI84RmUF39G7873","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const CLOUD = require('./config/cloud')\r\n\r\nApp({\r\n  globalData: {\r\n    pendingRecord: null,\r\n    pendingImportPath: '',\r\n    pendingImportName: '',\r\n    pendingDetectResult: null\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  onLaunch(options) {\r\n    if (wx.cloud && CLOUD.ENV_ID) {\r\n      wx.cloud.init({\r\n        env: CLOUD.ENV_ID,\r\n        traceUser: true\r\n      })\r\n    }\r\n    if (wx.setInnerAudioOption) {\r\n      wx.setInnerAudioOption({\r\n        obeyMuteSwitch: false,\r\n        mixWithOther: true\r\n      })\r\n    }\r\n    this.captureForwardFile(options)\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  onShow(options) {\r\n    this.captureForwardFile(options)\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  captureForwardFile(options) {\r\n    const materials = (options && options.forwardMaterials) || []\r\n    const file = materials.find((item) => item.type === 'file' && item.path)\r\n    if (!file) return\r\n\r\n    this.globalData.pendingImportPath = file.path\r\n    this.globalData.pendingImportName = file.name || ''\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  consumePendingImport() {\r\n    const path = this.globalData.pendingImportPath\r\n    const name = this.globalData.pendingImportName\r\n    this.globalData.pendingImportPath = ''\r\n    this.globalData.pendingImportName = ''\r\n    if (!path) return null\r\n    return { path, name }\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  setPendingDetect(result) {\r\n    this.globalData.pendingDetectResult = result\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  consumePendingDetect() {\r\n    const result = this.globalData.pendingDetectResult\r\n    this.globalData.pendingDetectResult = null\r\n    return result\r\n  }\r\n})"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":231,"aggregated":"const CLOUD = require('./config/cloud')\r\n\r\nApp({\r\n  globalData: {\r\n    pendingRecord: null,\r\n    pendingImportPath: '',\r\n    pendingImportName: '',\r\n    pendingDetectResult: null\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  onLaunch(options) {\r\n    if (wx.cloud && CLOUD.ENV_ID) {\r\n      wx.cloud.init({\r\n        env: CLOUD.ENV_ID,\r\n        traceUser: true\r\n      })\r\n    }\r\n    if (wx.setInnerAudioOption) {\r\n      wx.setInnerAudioOption({\r\n        obeyMuteSwitch: false,\r\n        mixWithOther: true\r\n      })\r\n    }\r\n    this.captureForwardFile(options)\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  onShow(options) {\r\n    this.captureForwardFile(options)\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  captureForwardFile(options) {\r\n    const materials = (options && options.forwardMaterials) || []\r\n    const file = materials.find((item) => item.type === 'file' && item.path)\r\n    if (!file) return\r\n\r\n    this.globalData.pendingImportPath = file.path\r\n    this.globalData.pendingImportName = file.name || ''\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  consumePendingImport() {\r\n    const path = this.globalData.pendingImportPath\r\n    const name = this.globalData.pendingImportName\r\n    this.globalData.pendingImportPath = ''\r\n    this.globalData.pendingImportName = ''\r\n    if (!path) return null\r\n    return { path, name }\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  setPendingDetect(result) {\r\n    this.globalData.pendingDetectResult = result\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  consumePendingDetect() {\r\n    const result = this.globalData.pendingDetectResult\r\n    this.globalData.pendingDetectResult = null\r\n    return result\r\n  }\r\n})","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781089097950}}
