{"type":"message","id":"678b6ddb","parentId":"a1c71255","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:58:34.476Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cloud functions folder is empty. Let me also check the cloudbase container debug.json for any clue about existing cloud functions.\n\nLet me now plan the implementation:\n\n1. Create a cloud function `login` that handles `wx.login()` code exchange via `jscode2session`\n2. Add login UI to the settings page (or create a dedicated login page)\n3. Use the Mini Program's own appid (`wx09786c3fb9eac9a4`) for the WeChat login - this is the standard Mini Program flow\n\nWait, actually the user said \"使用相关信息进行微信登录\". The \"相关信息\" from the APK analysis are:\n- `WX_APP_ID = \"wxd506e81fe975a813\"` (野狐围棋的微信开放平台 AppID)\n- `WX_APP_SECRET = \"e9d5f2…82cf\"` (野狐围棋的微信 AppSecret)\n\nIf the user wants to directly use these to call the WeChat API from the Mini Program, that won't work because:\n1. Mini Program's `wx.login()` uses the Mini Program's own appid, not an Open Platform appid\n2. The WeChat Open Platform AppID/Secret is for the 野狐围棋 app, not the Mini Program\n\nBut maybe the user wants to:\n- Use `wx.login()` → get code\n- Call their own cloud function with the code\n- The cloud function calls `https://api.weixin.qq.com/sns/jscode2session` using the Mini Program's appid+secret to get openid\n- Use the openid to then log in to 野狐围棋 service?\n\nActually, I think the simplest interpretation is: the user wants to add WeChat login functionality to their Mini Program using the standard Mini Program WeChat login flow. Let me just build that.\n\nLet me create:\n1. A cloud function for login\n2. A user service module\n3. Update the settings page with login UI\n4. Store the user state\n\nLet me also look at the cloudbase config file to see if there's a proper env setup.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HhyMMky4VAb6l0RTup0R9003","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\.cloudbase\\container\\debug.json\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":455,"output":550,"cacheRead":90752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91757,"cost":{"input":0.0000637,"output":0.000154,"cacheRead":0.002541056,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002758756}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781089108337,"responseId":"9b8939a9-a53c-40ae-8592-5ff1cdb07d41"}}
