{"type":"message","id":"e68442c0","parentId":"cdd5918d","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:58:42.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No cloud functions exist yet. Let me now plan out the implementation thoroughly:\n\n**Architecture:**\n1. `cloudbase/all/functions/login/` - Cloud function that calls `jscode2session` to get openid\n2. `miniprogram/services/auth.js` - Service module for login state management\n3. Update `pages/settings/settings` pages with login button and user info display\n\nLet me create the cloud function first. For the cloud function, I need to use the Mini Program's appid and secret. However, in Tencent CloudBase, the `jscode2session` API can be called using the cloud's built-in `cloud.getWXContext()` to get the openid without needing the secret. But if we want to call the WeChat API directly, we'd need the appid and secret.\n\nActually, in the WeChat Mini Program cloud development environment, you can get the user's openid directly from `wx.cloud.callFunction()` using `cloud.getWXContext()`. The cloud function automatically has access to the WeChat session context.\n\nLet me use this approach:\n1. Cloud function `login`: Uses `cloud.getWXContext()` to get `OPENID` and `UNIONID`\n2. Client calls `wx.login()` + `wx.cloud.callFunction()`\n3. Store the user info in `wx.setStorageSync()`\n\nLet me also check if there's a wx cloud function SDK initialized.\n\nLet me create the files now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来给你的小程序加上微信登录功能。先创建云函数处理登录，再更新前端页面。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9P6C8qQImo1PKkmXlCg66838","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Create cloud function directory\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\cloudbase\\all\\functions\\login\" -Force | Out-Null\n\n# Create package.json for cloud function\n@\"\n{\n  \"name\": \"login\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"微信登录\",\n  \"main\": \"index.js\",\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"wx-server-sdk\": \"latest\"\n  }\n}\n\"@ | Out-File -FilePath \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\cloudbase\\all\\functions\\login\\package.json\" -Encoding utf8\n\n# Create index.js for cloud function\n@\"\nconst cloud = require('wx-server-sdk')\ncloud.init()\n\nexports.main = async (event, context) => {\n  const { OPENID, UNIONID, APPID } = cloud.getWXContext()\n  \n  // 这里可以接入自己的后端或数据库\n  // 目前 simple 实现：用 openid 作为用户标识\n  return {\n    code: 0,\n    data: {\n      openid: OPENID,\n      unionid: UNIONID || '',\n      appid: APPID,\n      // 模拟用户信息（后续可对接数据库）\n      nickName: event.nickName || '棋友',\n      avatarUrl: event.avatarUrl || '',\n    },\n    msg: 'ok'\n  }\n}\n\"@ | Out-File -FilePath \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\cloudbase\\all\\functions\\login\\index.js\" -Encoding utf8\n\nWrite-Host \"Cloud function created\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":130,"output":773,"cacheRead":91648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92551,"cost":{"input":0.000018200000000000002,"output":0.00021644,"cacheRead":0.002566144,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0028007839999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781089114724,"responseId":"d755ae0a-8aab-4505-80a4-140f50cfad5e"}}
