{"type":"message","id":"e43e34e6","parentId":"00921503","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:59:33.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No cloud config in app.json. In WeChat Mini Programs using CloudBase, the cloud capability is typically enabled through the IDE's cloud settings or via `app.json` with a `\"cloudbase\"` field for newer versions.\n\nHowever, looking at the app.js, it already initializes `wx.cloud` with the ENV_ID from config, which is the standard way to do it. The cloud functions can be called by name after initialization.\n\nNow let me also create a default-avatar.png for when the user doesn't have an avatar. Actually, I'll just use an inline SVG or a text fallback instead.\n\nLet me also make sure the cloud function has the proper structure by checking the cloudbase's current configuration.\n\nLet me also verify the final file structure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_7A45Dja9IC6ACwad15me0774","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Verify all the files I created\nWrite-Host \"=== Cloud function ===\"\nGet-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\cloudbase\\all\\functions\\login\\index.js\"\nWrite-Host \"=== Auth service ===\"\nGet-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\miniprogram\\services\\auth.js\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":51,"output":317,"cacheRead":98432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98800,"cost":{"input":0.00000714,"output":0.00008876000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002756096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002851996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781089169661,"responseId":"7b8f4a8e-a599-4de2-8dc7-0b4e8cc213c4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ee9a346","parentId":"e43e34e6","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:59:33.894Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_7A45Dja9IC6ACwad15me0774","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Cloud function ===\nconst cloud = require('wx-server-sdk')\r\ncloud.init()\r\n\r\nexports.main = async (event, context) => {\r\n  const { OPENID, UNIONID, APPID } = cloud.getWXContext()\r\n  \r\n  // 这里可以接入自己的后端或数据库\r\n  // 目前 simple 实现：用 openid 作为用户标识\r\n  return {\r\n    code: 0,\r\n    data: {\r\n      openid: OPENID,\r\n      unionid: UNIONID || '',\r\n      appid: APPID,\r\n      // 模拟用户信息（后续可对接数据库）\r\n      nickName: event.nickName || '棋友',\r\n      avatarUrl: event.avatarUrl || '',\r\n    },\r\n    msg: 'ok'\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n=== Auth service ===\n/**\r\n * 寰俊鐧诲綍鏈嶅姟\r\n * 鏀寔闈欓粯鐧诲綍鍜屽甫鐢ㄦ埛淇℃伅鐨勬巿鏉冪櫥褰? */\r\n\r\nconst AUTH_STORAGE_KEY = '***'\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 闈欓粯鐧诲綍锛氳幏鍙?openid锛屼笉寮规巿鏉冩\r\n */\r\nasync function silentLogin() {\r\n  try {\r\n    // 鍏堟鏌ユ湰鍦版槸鍚﹀凡鏈夌櫥褰曟€?    const cached = getCachedUser()\r\n    if (cached && cached.openid) {\r\n      return cached\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    const { code } = await wx.login()\r\n    if (!code) {\r\n      console.error('[auth] wx.login failed: no code')\r\n      return null\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    const result = await wx.cloud.callFunction({\r\n      name: 'login',\r\n      data: { code }\r\n    })\r\n\r\n    if (result.result && result.result.code === 0) {\r\n      const user = result.result.data\r\n      cacheUser(user)\r\n      return user\r\n    }\r\n    return null\r\n  } catch (err) {\r\n    console.error('[auth] silentLogin error:', err)\r\n    return null\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 瀹屾暣寰俊鐧诲綍锛氬脊鍑烘巿鏉冩鑾峰彇鐢ㄦ埛鏄电О澶村儚\r\n */\r\nasync function fullLogin() {\r\n  try {\r\n    // 鍏堥潤榛樼櫥褰曡幏鍙?openid\r\n    let user = await silentLogin()\r\n    if (!user) return null\r\n\r\n    // 寮规巿鏉冩鑾峰彇鏄电О鍜屽ご鍍?    const setting = await wx.getSetting()\r\n    if (setting.authSetting['scope.userInfo']) {\r\n      // 宸叉湁鎺堟潈锛岀洿鎺ヨ幏鍙?      const userInfoRes = await wx.getUserInfo({\r\n        lang: 'zh_CN'\r\n      })\r\n      user.nickName = userInfoRes.userInfo.nickName\r\n      user.avatarUrl = userInfoRes.userInfo.avatarUrl\r\n    } else {\r\n      // 闇€瑕佺敤鎴风偣鍑绘巿鏉?      // 杩欑鎯呭喌寤鸿鐢?button open-type=\"getUserInfo\" 瑙﹀彂\r\n      // 杩欓噷鍙仛闈欓粯閮ㄥ垎\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    cacheUser(user)\r\n    return user\r\n  } catch (err) {\r\n    console.error('[auth] fullLogin error:', err)\r\n    return null\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 鑾峰彇缂撳瓨鐢ㄦ埛\r\n */\r\nfunction getCachedUser() {\r\n  try {\r\n    const raw = wx.getStorageSync(AUTH_STORAGE_KEY)\r\n    if (raw) {\r\n      return JSON.parse(raw)\r\n    }\r\n  } catch (e) {\r\n    // ignore\r\n  }\r\n  return null\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 缂撳瓨鐢ㄦ埛\r\n */\r\nfunction cacheUser(user) {\r\n  wx.setStorageSync(AUTH_STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(user))\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 閫€鍑虹櫥褰? */\r\nfunction logout() {\r\n  try {\r\n    wx.removeStorageSync(AUTH_STORAGE_KEY)\r\n  } catch (e) {\r\n    // ignore\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 鏄惁宸茬櫥褰? */\r\nfunction isLoggedIn() {\r\n  return !!getCachedUser()\r\n}\r\n\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  silentLogin,\r\n  fullLogin,\r\n  getCachedUser,\r\n  logout,\r\n  isLoggedIn\r\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":269,"aggregated":"=== Cloud function ===\nconst cloud = require('wx-server-sdk')\r\ncloud.init()\r\n\r\nexports.main = async (event, context) => {\r\n  const { OPENID, UNIONID, APPID } = cloud.getWXContext()\r\n  \r\n  // 这里可以接入自己的后端或数据库\r\n  // 目前 simple 实现：用 openid 作为用户标识\r\n  return {\r\n    code: 0,\r\n    data: {\r\n      openid: OPENID,\r\n      unionid: UNIONID || '',\r\n      appid: APPID,\r\n      // 模拟用户信息（后续可对接数据库）\r\n      nickName: event.nickName || '棋友',\r\n      avatarUrl: event.avatarUrl || '',\r\n    },\r\n    msg: 'ok'\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n=== Auth service ===\n/**\r\n * 寰俊鐧诲綍鏈嶅姟\r\n * 鏀寔闈欓粯鐧诲綍鍜屽甫鐢ㄦ埛淇℃伅鐨勬巿鏉冪櫥褰? */\r\n\r\nconst AUTH_STORAGE_KEY = 'weiqi_auth_user'\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 闈欓粯鐧诲綍锛氳幏鍙?openid锛屼笉寮规巿鏉冩\r\n */\r\nasync function silentLogin() {\r\n  try {\r\n    // 鍏堟鏌ユ湰鍦版槸鍚﹀凡鏈夌櫥褰曟€?    const cached = getCachedUser()\r\n    if (cached && cached.openid) {\r\n      return cached\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    const { code } = await wx.login()\r\n    if (!code) {\r\n      console.error('[auth] wx.login failed: no code')\r\n      return null\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    const result = await wx.cloud.callFunction({\r\n      name: 'login',\r\n      data: { code }\r\n    })\r\n\r\n    if (result.result && result.result.code === 0) {\r\n      const user = result.result.data\r\n      cacheUser(user)\r\n      return user\r\n    }\r\n    return null\r\n  } catch (err) {\r\n    console.error('[auth] silentLogin error:', err)\r\n    return null\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 瀹屾暣寰俊鐧诲綍锛氬脊鍑烘巿鏉冩鑾峰彇鐢ㄦ埛鏄电О澶村儚\r\n */\r\nasync function fullLogin() {\r\n  try {\r\n    // 鍏堥潤榛樼櫥褰曡幏鍙?openid\r\n    let user = await silentLogin()\r\n    if (!user) return null\r\n\r\n    // 寮规巿鏉冩鑾峰彇鏄电О鍜屽ご鍍?    const setting = await wx.getSetting()\r\n    if (setting.authSetting['scope.userInfo']) {\r\n      // 宸叉湁鎺堟潈锛岀洿鎺ヨ幏鍙?      const userInfoRes = await wx.getUserInfo({\r\n        lang: 'zh_CN'\r\n      })\r\n      user.nickName = userInfoRes.userInfo.nickName\r\n      user.avatarUrl = userInfoRes.userInfo.avatarUrl\r\n    } else {\r\n      // 闇€瑕佺敤鎴风偣鍑绘巿鏉?      // 杩欑鎯呭喌寤鸿鐢?button open-type=\"getUserInfo\" 瑙﹀彂\r\n      // 杩欓噷鍙仛闈欓粯閮ㄥ垎\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    cacheUser(user)\r\n    return user\r\n  } catch (err) {\r\n    console.error('[auth] fullLogin error:', err)\r\n    return null\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 鑾峰彇缂撳瓨鐢ㄦ埛\r\n */\r\nfunction getCachedUser() {\r\n  try {\r\n    const raw = wx.getStorageSync(AUTH_STORAGE_KEY)\r\n    if (raw) {\r\n      return JSON.parse(raw)\r\n    }\r\n  } catch (e) {\r\n    // ignore\r\n  }\r\n  return null\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 缂撳瓨鐢ㄦ埛\r\n */\r\nfunction cacheUser(user) {\r\n  wx.setStorageSync(AUTH_STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(user))\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 閫€鍑虹櫥褰? */\r\nfunction logout() {\r\n  try {\r\n    wx.removeStorageSync(AUTH_STORAGE_KEY)\r\n  } catch (e) {\r\n    // ignore\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 鏄惁宸茬櫥褰? */\r\nfunction isLoggedIn() {\r\n  return !!getCachedUser()\r\n}\r\n\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  silentLogin,\r\n  fullLogin,\r\n  getCachedUser,\r\n  logout,\r\n  isLoggedIn\r\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781089173894}}
{"type":"message","id":"8342fe1e","parentId":"1ee9a346","timestamp":"2026-06-10T10:59:39.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The files look good. The encoding comment at the top of auth.js is showing garbled text because I used UTF-8 without BOM and the Chinese comments got mangled. Let me fix that by rewriting with proper encoding.\n\nActually, this is the `write` tool that already encoded content. The garbled text might just be how it's displayed in PowerShell. Let me verify by checking actual bytes.\n\nActually, looking at the file output, the Chinese comments are garbled. The `write` tool created the content as I specified (UTF-8), and when PowerShell reads it back, it displays the Chinese incorrectly because PowerShell's console doesn't output UTF-8 Chinese properly.\n\nThe actual file content should be correct since I wrote it with `-Encoding utf8` in the write tool. The garbled display is just a console encoding issue.\n\nLet me also check the settings page files and verify everything is connected.\n\nLet me also create a default avatar SVG/icon.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_SJoVqRiwasAqE5gOERdW3344","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Verify Chinese text is correct by showing byte length\nWrite-Host \"Auth.js encoding check:\"\n(Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\miniprogram\\services\\auth.js\" -Encoding UTF8 | Select-Object -First 1).Length\nWrite-Host \"Settings.js encoding check:\"\n(Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\miniprogram\\pages\\settings\\settings.js\" -Encoding UTF8 | Select-Object -First 1).Length\n\n# Check if there's an existing icons directory for default avatar\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\miniprogram\\assets\\icons\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-f