{"type":"message","id":"4409dee8","parentId":"0c5ad12d","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:00:13.006Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the goban component is already registered in the settings page json. Everything looks correct.\n\nLet me now summarize the changes I made for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了！小结一下实现的内容：\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 微信登录已接入\n\n### 新增/修改的文件\n\n| 文件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `cloudbase/all/functions/login/index.js` | **新增** 云函数：通过 `wx-server-sdk` 的 `cloud.getWXContext()` 获取用户的 openid |\n| `cloudbase/all/functions/login/package.json` | **新增** 云函数依赖描述 |\n| `miniprogram/services/auth.js` | **新增** 登录服务模块（静默登录、缓存管理、退出） |\n| `miniprogram/pages/settings/settings.js` | **修改** 增加登录状态管理和按钮事件 |\n| `miniprogram/pages/settings/settings.wxml` | **修改** 增加登录面板 UI |\n| `miniprogram/pages/settings/settings.wxss` | **修改** 增加登录面板样式 |\n\n### 登录流程\n\n```\n用户点击\"微信登录\"按钮\n  → 弹出 WeChat 授权框（获取昵称+头像）\n  → wx.login() 获取临时 code\n  → 调云函数 login（传递 code + 用户信息）\n    → getWXContext() 自动解析出 openid/session_key\n    → 返回 { openid, nickName, avatarUrl }\n  → 缓存到 wx.setStorageSync\n  → 设置页面显示已登录状态（头像+昵称+退出按钮）\n```\n\n### 使用方式\n\n1. 在微信开发者工具中，**右键** `cloudbase/all/functions/login` → **创建并部署**（或上传并部署）\n2. 重新编译小程序，到设置页就能看到**微信登录**按钮\n3. 点一下授权登录即可\n\n### 后续扩展\n\n当前登录只做了基础数据交换，没有对接数据库。如果你需要：\n- **持久化用户数据** → 在云函数里加数据库写入\n- **对接野狐围棋** → 可以用拿到的 openid 去调野狐后端 API（如果他们有开放接口）\n- **多端同步用户收藏的棋谱** → 建一个 user_sgf 集合，关联 openid 即可\n\n需要继续加哪些功能？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":85,"output":509,"cacheRead":104320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104914,"cost":{"input":0.000011900000000000001,"output":0.00014252,"cacheRead":0.00292096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00307538}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781089206339,"responseId":"318db756-9e12-424c-865a-5e6cd4d3d028"}}
