{"type":"message","id":"390195a0","parentId":"429acbfa","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:06:31.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is changing the topic. They want me to reverse engineer the \"拍照数字\" (photo number) API from the 野狐围棋 app. This refers to the feature where the app takes a photo of a Go board (碁盤) and uses number/character recognition.\n\nLet me look back at the APK structure - there were references to face detection libraries (like YTCommonLiveness) and various detection-related so files. But more importantly, from the cloudrun directory in the Mini Program project, I can see there's already a `weiqi-detect` service that does Go board detection.\n\nActually, looking at this from the APK perspective, the \"拍照数字\" feature might be about recognizing numbers on a Go board (like the coordinate numbers) or something related to OCR/digit recognition on Go photos.\n\nLet me look at the relevant parts of the APK for number/digit recognition APIs. The best approach would be to look at:\n1. The libil2cpp.so for any digit/OCR related strings\n2. The native libraries that might be used for image processing\n3. The Java bridge code for camera-related features\n\nLet me check the MainActivity for camera-related methods and also look at the native libraries that might be involved.\n\nActually, let me check what I already found about the camera:\n- MainActivity has `_OpenCamera`, `_OpenGallery`, `_SaveImageToGallery` methods\n- Native libraries include: `libkyctoolkit.so`, `libYTCommonLiveness.so` (face detection/liveness), `libttmplayer_lite.so` (video player)\n- The cloudrun weiqi-detect service already exists\n\nLet me search more specifically for digit/number recognition in the APK.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，来看看野狐围棋的拍照数字识别 API。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_rfFbI9yvSVhy3AGXmkev0208","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Search for digit/recognition/OCR related strings in the binary\n$path = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\lib\\arm64-v8a\\libil2cpp.so\"\n\n$patterns = @(\"digit\", \"Detect\", \"detect\", \"recogni\", \"ocr\", \"OCR\", \n              \"number\", \"Number\", \"ImageProc\", \"imageProc\", \"photo\",\n              \"paddle\", \"opencv\", \"tensor\", \"onnx\", \"ncnn\",\n              \"binary\", \"contour\", \"segment\", \"crop\", \"resize\",\n              \"Upload\", \"upload\", \"compress\", \"image\")\n\nforeach ($pattern in $patterns) {\n    $matches = Select-String -Path $path -Pattern $pattern -SimpleMatch -AllMatches 2>$null\n    $allMatches = @($matches)\n    if ($allMatches.Count -gt 0) {\n        Write-Host \"Found '$pattern' ($($allMatches.Count) matches):\"\n        $allMatches | Select-Object -First 3 | ForEach-Object { \n            $line = $_.Line.Trim()\n            if ($line.Length -gt 30) { $line = $line.Substring(0, 30) + \"...\" }\n            Write-Host \"  $line\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"=== Camera-related methods in MainActivity ===\"\n$maLines = Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\smali_classes3\\com\\foxwq\\yhwq\\MainActivity.smali\"\n$maLines | Where-Object { $_ -match \"\\.method|OpenCamera|OpenGallery|SaveImage|camera|Camera|photo|Photo|Uri|compress|bitmap|Bitmap\" } | Select-Object -First 20","timeout":60,"yieldMs":15000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":56222,"output":850,"cacheRead":98816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155888,"cost":{"input":0.00787108,"output":0.000238,"cacheRead":0.002766848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010875928000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781089581713,"responseId":"e640ce8e-5195-4b31-8fd8-a968b5bc0d42"}}
