{"type":"message","id":"945fa9b4","parentId":"5ffd55ac","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:07:04.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Java code in MainActivity is mainly about camera/gallery operations for taking photos and cropping images - it doesn't directly do number/digit recognition. It just captures/crops images and passes them to Unity.\n\nThe actual number recognition (\"拍照数字\" = photo number/digit) is likely done in the Unity C# code (IL2CPP), and the recognition might be using:\n1. A cloud-based OCR API (which would be in the Unity code)\n2. A local model using ONNX/TensorFlow Lite (which would be in the libil2cpp.so or as separate .so files)\n\nFrom the native libraries I found earlier, relevant ones include:\n- `libkyctoolkit.so` - KYC toolkit (likely for face recognition/document scanning)\n- `libYTCommonLiveness.so` - Face liveness detection\n- `libturingmfa.so` - Turing MFA (multi-factor authentication)\n\nNone of these seem to be Go-related number recognition.\n\nThe user specifically said \"拍照数字api\" - photo number API. This could mean:\n1. The API endpoint for uploading a photo and getting recognized numbers back\n2. The API that detects game board position numbers\n\nSince they want the API and this is the 野狐围棋 app, the most likely interpretation is the Go board photo recognition API - you take a photo of a physical Go board and it detects the stone positions.\n\nLet me look at the FGUI files for any UI related to photo detection.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_t6v2VmXjWE0FIEYe9b5k6958","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Search FGUI for photo/scan/recognize related UI\nSelect-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\assets\\FGUI\\ChineseSimplified.xml\" -Pattern \"拍照|扫描|识别|上传|照片|相册|相机|棋盘|棋谱|导入\" | Select-Object -First 30\n\nWrite-Host \"=== I18N for photo-related ===\"\nSelect-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\assets\\I18N\\I18N.csv\" -Pattern \"拍照|扫描|识别|upload|Upload|photo|Photo|拍照|相机|camera|Camera|棋谱|导入\" | Select-Object -First 20","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2333,"output":526,"cacheRead":156416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":159275,"cost":{"input":0.00032662,"output":0.00014728,"cacheRead":0.004379648,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004853548}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781089616862,"responseId":"bd957654-bbad-41f1-abd0-cd9b9cb28709"}}
