{"type":"message","id":"ac14d514","parentId":"90cc4572","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:07:10.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The \"拍照数子\" feature (photo number counting). Key strings:\n- `拍照数子` - Photo number counting\n- `开始识别3S` - Starting recognition in 3 seconds\n- `请对着棋盘拍照` - Please take photo of the board\n- `识别频率过快，请稍后重试` - Recognition frequency too fast\n- `识别失败，您可尝试对照片截屏或使用野狐围棋拍照` - Recognition failed\n- `当前设备暂不支持拍照数子功能` - Device doesn't support this feature\n- `拍照取题` - Photo problem fetching\n\nThe UI is at `lovlj66mfurpv.xml` (in FGUI). Let me look at this XML file for more details about the API interaction.\n\nLet me also look in the FGUI folder for the specific XML files related to this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_H7dqIB8JKEMMqSYUVbi50884","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Find the FGUI component files related to photo counting\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\assets\\FGUI\" -Recurse -Filter \"*.xml\" | Where-Object { $_.Name -match \"furpv|lovlj|petph|dl7puk\" -or $_.Basename -match \"photo|Photo|scan|Scan|camera|Camera|number|Number\" } | Select-Object Name\n\nWrite-Host \"=== Components directory listing ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\assets\\FGUI\" -Depth 1 | Select-Object Mode, Name\n\nWrite-Host \"=== Look for any .def or package files ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\野狐围棋\\assets\\FGUI\" -Recurse -Include \"*.def\",\"*.bytes\",\"*.fui\",\"*.package\" | Select-Object Name, Length","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3728,"output":458,"cacheRead":159232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":163418,"cost":{"input":0.00052192,"output":0.00012824,"cacheRead":0.004458496,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0051086560000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781089624696,"responseId":"057e50d2-8e47-4fb1-b299-a21d