ease try later.\"\n: 继续重连,繼續重連,再接続を続行,??? ??,Continue reconnecting\n: 重连成功，对局已结束。,重連成功，對局已結束。,再接続成功、対局は終了しています。,\"??? ??, ?? ?????.\",\"Reconnected, game already ended.\"\n: 重连成功，玩家对局已结束。,重連成功，玩家對局已結束。,再接続成功、プレイヤーの対局は終了しています。,\"??? ??, ??? ?? ?????.\",\"Reconnected, player game already ended.\"\n: 升级失败，请确认网络连接和存储权限,升級失敗，請確認網絡連接和存儲權限,アップデート失敗、ネットワーク接続とストレージ権限を確認してください。,????? ??. ???? ?? ? ?? ??? ??? ???,\"Update failed, check network connection and storage permission\"\n: 失败：有对弈者掉线,失敗：有對弈者掉線,失敗：対局者が切断しました,??：??? ? ??? ?? ??? ????,Failed: player disconnected\n: 网络连接超时，请重试,網絡連接超時，請重試,ネットワーク接続タイムアウト、再試行してください,???? ?? ?? ??，?? ??? ???,\"Network connection timeout, please retry\"\n: 连接,連接,連接,連絡,??,Connection\n: 虎口,虎口,虎口,カケツギ,??,Hane-connect (Tiger’s mouth)[... 76761 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781089645353}}
{"type":"message","id":"a184b4aa","parentId":"6f7dfb6f","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:07:37.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, I've gathered enough data. The key discovered domains are:\n- `foxwq.com` - Main domain\n- `edu.foxwq.com` - VIP/education subdomain\n\nAnd the 拍照数子 feature is clearly part of the app. However, the actual API endpoint for the photo recognition is in the IL2CPP binary which I can't efficiently extract without proper tools.\n\nLet me now summarize what I've found and present it to the user. The actual API pathways for the photo number counting are stored in the Unity C# code. To get the exact endpoints, the user would need to:\n1. Use il2cppDumper + Ghidra/IDA Pro on libil2cpp.so\n2. Or capture network traffic while using the app\n\nLet me compile a comprehensive report.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，以下是逆向分析野狐围棋 **拍照数子** 功能的结果：\n\n---\n\n## 📸 拍照数子 功能分析\n\n### 功能描述\n\n\"拍照数子\"是野狐围棋的一个特色功能：**拍摄物理棋盘照片 → 自动识别棋子位置和数目**。\n\n### UI 相关字符串\n\n| 字符串 | 含义 |\n|--------|------|\n| `拍照数子功能在这里` | 入口提示 |\n| `拍照数子` | 功能名称 |\n| `请对着棋盘拍照` | 拍照提示 |\n| `开始识别3S` | 倒计时 3 秒开始识别 |\n| `识别频率过快，请稍后重试` | API 限流 |\n| `无法识别` | 识别失败 |\n| `识别失败，您可尝试对照片截屏` | 识别失败提示 |\n| `当前设备暂不支持拍照数子功能` | 设备兼容性检查 |\n| `拍照取题` | 相关功能 - 拍照提取题目 |\n| `野狐围棋-拍照数子` | 分享标题 |\n\n### 技术架构\n\n```\n用户拍棋盘 → Android Camera/相册\n        ↓ (Java bridge: _OpenCamera / _OpenGallery)\n   Unity C# (图像预处理)\n        ↓ (HTTP upload → 服务器端 AI 识别)\n   野狐后端 API → 返回 { 棋子位置, 数目, 胜负 }\n        ↓\n   Unity 渲染结果到 UI\n```\n\n### 已发现的服务器信息\n\n| 域名 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **foxwq.com** | 主域名 |\n| **edu.foxwq.com** | VIP/教育服务 |\n| `enterprise@foxwq.com` | 客服邮箱 |\n\n### 识别 API 端点\n\n> ⚠️ **拍照数子的具体 API 端点在 Unity IL2CPP 代码中（libil2cpp.so, 81MB）**，当前通过静态分析无法直接提取。\n\n---\n\n### 💡 获取精确 API 的两种方案\n\n**方案 A：il2cppDumper + IDA Pro**\n1. 用 il2cppDumper 提取 global-metadata.dat 的字符串表\n2. 用 IDA Pro / Ghidra 加载 libil2cpp.so\n3. 配合 dumped 的 metadata 恢复 C# 类名/方法名\n4. 搜索包含 `http`、`upload`、`recognize`、`photo`、`detect` 等关键字的字符串\n\n**方案 B：网络抓包（推荐，更快）**\n1. 在 Android 手机/模拟器上装 野狐围棋 + HttpCanary/Charles Proxy\n2. 抓取拍照数子功能的 HTTP 请求\n3. 分析请求 URL、参数、响应格式\n\n需要我装个模拟器来做网络抓包，拿到精确的 API 地址吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":42638,"output":790,"cacheRead":168064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":211492,"cost":{"input":0.00596932,"output":0.0002212,"cacheRead":0.004705792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010896312000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781089645357,"responseId":"a8ab9c64-ae8b-4e65-bc8f-456a4bc6f7b7"}}
