{"type":"message","id":"ef469f06","parentId":"3c655cae","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:53:29.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! The MuMu Player emulator is running and accessible. We have 3 devices:\n- `127.0.0.1:5555` - device\n- `127.0.0.1:7555` - device \n- `emulator-5554` - device\n\nThe emulator is MuMu Player 12.0 (Android 12). Now I need to:\n\n1. Install the 野狐围棋 APK on the emulator\n2. Set up mitmproxy for HTTPS capture\n\nBut first I need to install a proxy tool. Let me install mitmproxy since it's the best for HTTPS capture.\n\nActually wait - I have Python available (the check earlier showed python not available, but let me check again since we might have it). Actually Python wasn't found.\n\nLet me try a different approach - install Fiddler Classic (native Windows app, no dependencies) or use Node.js based proxy.\n\nActually, the fastest way might be to:\n1. Install mitmproxy via pip (need to install Python first)\n2. Or use a simpler approach\n\nLet me check if I can install Python quickly via winget, or use a pre-built Windows binary of mitmproxy.\n\nActually, mitmproxy has standalone Windows binaries. Let me check.\n\nOr even simpler - I could use **Charles Proxy** which is Java-based (we have Java!). Let me try that.\n\nActually, let me just install Python first - it's the most versatile option.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"模拟器已运行！先安装 Python 和 mitmproxy。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_erIGPO6R40gdaWaNtDml3636","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"winget install \"Python 3.12\" --accept-package-agreements --accept-source-agreements 2>&1","timeout":120,"yieldMs":20000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":429,"output":422,"cacheRead":163328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164179,"cost":{"input":0.000060060000000000004,"output":0.00011816000000000001,"cacheRead":0.004573184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004751404}},"