{"type":"message","id":"6688f517","parentId":"3d81c2ba","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:55:08.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"mitmproxy installed successfully. Now I need to:\n\n1. Set up the proxy on the emulator to use mitmproxy\n2. Install mitmproxy's CA certificate on the Android emulator for HTTPS decryption\n3. Run mitmproxy and capture the traffic\n\nLet me set this up. First, start mitmproxy, install the CA cert on the Android emulator, configure the proxy settings, then run the app and use the photo feature.\n\nActually, a simpler approach might be to use mitmweb (the web UI version of mitmproxy) which is easier to interact with.\n\nLet me first:\n1. Start mitmweb\n2. Configure Android emulator proxy\n3. Install the CA certificate\n4. Capture traffic\n\nLet me do this step by step. First, generate the CA certificate.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"mitmproxy 已装好。现在设置代理抓包。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_MxhDLtHDvdaO4cMVYkwL1298","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Start mitmweb in background to generate the CA cert\n$pythonDir = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\Scripts\"\n$env:Path = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312;$pythonDir;$env:Path\"\n\n# First run mitmproxy once to generate CA cert\nmitmproxy --version 2>&1\n\n# Find the CA cert\n$caCert = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.mitmproxy\\mitmproxy-ca-cert.cer\"\nif (Test-Path $caCert) {\n    Write-Host \"CA cert exists at $caCert\"\n} else {\n    # Generate it by briefly running mitmdump\n    Write-Host \"Generating CA cert...\"\n    $proc = Start-Process -NoNewWindow -FilePath \"mitmdump\" -PassThru\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 3\n    Stop-Process -Id $proc.Id -Force\n}\n\n# Check cert\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.mitmproxy\" | Select-Object Name, Length","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4691,"output":490,"cacheRead":167296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":172477,"cost":{"input":0.0006567400000000001,"output":0.0001372,"cacheRead":0.004684288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005478228}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781092503007,"responseId":"3e056566-d269-43e2-85c8-ab3758a0717f"}}
