{"type":"message","id":"a2dd3b19","parentId":"989c97cc","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:59:13.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"mitmweb is running on port 8080 (proxy) and 8081 (web UI). Now I need to:\n\n1. Configure the Android emulator's WiFi proxy to point to `10.0.2.2:8080`\n2. Run the app and use the photo number feature\n3. Capture the API calls\n\nLet me configure the proxy on the emulator using ADB.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"mitmproxy 已启动。现在配置模拟器的代理。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_QyjGm7CgV8hrZxEQngSj5970","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$adb = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\\platform-tools\\adb.exe\"\n\n# Set up proxy on the emulator using iptables (root)\n# Redirect all outgoing traffic on ports 80 and 443 to mitmproxy on host\nWrite-Host \"Setting up iptables redirect...\"\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"su -c 'iptables -t nat -F'\" 2>&1 | Out-Null\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"su -c 'iptables -t nat -A OUTPUT -p tcp --dport 80 -j REDIRECT --to-port 8080'\" 2>&1\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"su -c 'iptables -t nat -A OUTPUT -p tcp --dport 443 -j REDIRECT --to-port 8080'\" 2>&1\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"su -c 'iptables -t nat -L -n'\" 2>&1\n\n# Also add a route to make 10.0.2.2 accessible\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"su -c 'ip route add 10.0.2.0/24 via 10.0.2.2 dev wlan0'\" 2>&1\n\n# Verify\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"su -c 'ip route'\" 2>&1\n\nWrite-Host \"Proxy configured. Now launch the app...\"\n# Launch the app\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"monkey -p com.foxwq.yhwq -c android.intent.category.LAUNCHER 1\" 2>&1\n\nWrite-Host \"App launched! Use the photo counting feature.\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":309,"output":616,"cacheRead":191104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":192029,"cost":{