{"type":"message","id":"af10851d","parentId":"20033139","timestamp":"2026-06-10T11:59:21.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The app was launched. The iptables rules are set up. But there's a problem - the REDIRECT target only works for traffic going through the local machine. Since the emulator's iptables OUTPUT chain is redirecting to port 8080, but the mitmproxy is on the host (not the emulator), this won't work.\n\nThe REDIRECT target redirects the packet to a local port on the same machine. Since mitmproxy is running on the host (not the emulator), I need a different approach.\n\nI need to either:\n1. Run mitmproxy on the emulator (push it as a binary)\n2. Use a forward proxy: set the Android WiFi proxy to 10.0.2.2:8080 (this is the standard way)\n3. Use NAT redirect (DNAT) instead of REDIRECT\n\nOption 2 is the simplest - set the WiFi proxy. Let me configure the WiFi settings.\n\nFor Android 12 emulator, I can set the global proxy settings using ADB:\n```\nadb shell settings put global http_proxy 10.0.2.2:8080\n```\n\nLet me try this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_D7RJq7vBhyntZIn3ynzk8077","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$adb = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\\platform-tools\\adb.exe\"\n\n# Clear iptables rules first\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"su -c 'iptables -t nat -F'\" 2>&1 | Out-Null\n\n# Set the Android global HTTP proxy to the host's mitmproxy\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"settings put global http_proxy 10.0.2.2:8080\" 2>&1\n\n# Verify\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"settings get global http_proxy\" 2>&1\n\n# Check if the app is running\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"ps | grep foxwq\" 2>&1\n\nWrite-Host \"Proxy configured as forward proxy. Open the app manually and use the photo number feature.\"\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"mitmweb UI: http://127.0.0.1:8081/\"\nWrite-Host \"Token: 9e265f6c9876bfee9888847a90fe061f\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":750,"output":597,"cacheRead":192000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":193347,"cost":{"input":0.000105,"output":0.00016716000000000002,"cacheRead":0.005376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005648159999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781092754498,"responseId":"51f82c76-5294-4c12-b86a-77ac2dd586c6"}}
