{"type":"message","id":"a9ea0f93","parentId":"128fee1b","timestamp":"2026-06-10T12:00:14.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! I can see the flows! The API is working with the token. I can see:\n\n1. A flow to `api.mumu.nie.netease.com` - This is the MuMu emulator's own update API checking for the app, not the 野狐围棋 API.\n\n2. The mitmproxy is capturing traffic. The SSL connection to `api.mumu.nie.netease.com` succeeded (it's using mitmproxy's cert).\n\nBut I need the actual 野狐围棋 traffic. The app just launched and may not have made its API calls yet. Let me:\n1. Wait a bit more for the app to fully load\n2. Check for more flows\n3. Also check the Unity logs for network-related text\n\nLet me poll the flows again.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ycJ9tA8bZZA05a9Q4SZ24659","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$adb = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\\platform-tools\\adb.exe\"\n$token = \"9e265f6c9876bfee9888847a90fe061f\"\n$flowsUrl = \"http://127.0.0.1:8081/flows?token=$token\"\n\n# Wait for more traffic\nStart-Sleep 5\n\n# Get fresh flows\ntry {\n    $flows = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri $flowsUrl -TimeoutSec 5\n    Write-Host \"=== Captured Flows ($($flows.Count)) ===\"\n    $flows | ForEach-Object {\n        Write-Host \"$($_.request.method) $($_.request.host)$($_.request.path)\"\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"Error: $_\"\n}\n\n# Also check Unity logs\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"=== Recent Unity Logs ===\"\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 logcat -d -s \"Unity\" 2>&1 | Select-Object -Last 20","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":547,"output":478,"cacheRead":198528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":199553,"cost":{"input":0.00007658,"output":0.00013384,"cacheRead":0.005558784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005769204}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp