{"type":"message","id":"c3ac3ac1","parentId":"8339b2de","timestamp":"2026-06-10T12:05:57.993Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"GitHub search is not returning useful results - it's just showing the login page. Let me try a different approach - try to find the 涨棋网 mini program by looking at its WeChat appid or known endpoints.\n\nActually, 涨棋网 is a popular WeChat Mini Program for Go. Let me look for it differently. Let me try to extract the mini program from my WeChat developer tools.\n\nActually, wait. The user said \"先看看涨棋网小程序的拍照数子接口\" - they want to look at the 涨棋网 mini program's photo number API. This might mean:\n1. They have the 涨棋网 source code available somewhere\n2. They want me to find the API by looking at how the mini program works\n3. Or they want me to analyze a downloaded/packaged version of the mini program\n\nLet me check if there's a downloaded wxapkg (WeChat Mini Program package) somewhere.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_1mFu74nBWyhli4RiFdFN5179","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Search for wxapkg files (unpackaged WeChat Mini Programs) or mini program code\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\" -Recurse -Depth 5 -Include \"*.wxapkg\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object FullName, Length | Sort-Object Length -Descending | Select-Object -First 10\n\nWrite-Host \"---\"\n# Also check WeChat dev tools storage\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\微信开发者工具\" -Recurse -Depth 6 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | \n    Where-Object { $_.PSIsContainer -and $_.Name -match \"涨棋|zhangqi\" } | Select-Object FullName\n\nWrite-Host \"---\"\n# Search for any zhangqi related miniprogram directories\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\" -Directory -Recurse -Depth 5 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | \n    Where-Object { $_.Name -match \"涨棋|zhangqi|zqw\" } | Select-Object FullName","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"d