{"type":"message","id":"e21529e7","parentId":"b12a886b","timestamp":"2026-06-10T12:06:22.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Web pages aren't returning useful content due to the fetch limitations. Let me try to find the 涨棋网 mini program by searching for it in a more targeted way.\n\nActually, the user's mini program already has a `cloudrun/weiqi-detect/` service with Python code for Go board detection. Let me look at that code to understand how it works - it's probably similar to what 涨棋网 uses for photo number detection.\n\nLet me read the existing detect code to understand the API pattern, and also let me look at the problem-bank service which might reference the 涨棋网 API.\n\nActually, let me also try to see if I can access the 涨棋网 mini program directly through the WeChat developer tools since the user has it installed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"涨棋网的源文件没找到。不过你的项目里已经有 `cloudrun/weiqi-detect/` 围棋检测服务，我来看看它的 API 结构和涨棋网的关联。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CwDaJC4x8mwCovHxzPO55362","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check the cloudrun detect service code\nGet-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\cloudrun\\weiqi-detect\\app.py\" -Head 100\n\nWrite-Host \"=== detect service files ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\cloudrun\\weiqi-detect\" -File | Select-Object Name, Length\n\nWrite-Host \"=== check miniprogram services for API calls ===\"\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\miniprogram\\services\" -File | Select-Object Name, Length","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1657,"output":421,"cacheRead":219520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":221598,"cost":{"input":0.00023198,"output":0.00011788,"cacheRead":0.00614656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006496419999999999}},"stopReason":"toolU