{"type":"message","id":"14a9fb98","parentId":"e21529e7","timestamp":"2026-06-10T12:06:22.537Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_CwDaJC4x8mwCovHxzPO55362","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"from flask import Flask, jsonify, request\r\n\r\nfrom baduk_detect import detect_board_baduk, suggest_corners\r\nfrom image_decode import decode_image\r\nfrom moku_detect import is_ready as moku_ready\r\n\r\napp = Flask(__name__)\r\nVERSION = \"5.0.0\"\r\n\r\n\r\ndef health_payload():\r\n    return {\r\n        \"ok\": True,\r\n        \"service\": \"weiqi-detect\",\r\n        \"version\": VERSION,\r\n        \"detector\": \"baduk\",\r\n        \"mokuReady\": moku_ready(),\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n@app.route(\"/\", methods=[\"GET\", \"POST\"])\r\ndef root():\r\n    return jsonify(health_payload())\r\n\r\n\r\n@app.route(\"/health\", methods=[\"GET\", \"POST\"])\r\n@app.route(\"/health/\", methods=[\"GET\", \"POST\"])\r\ndef health():\r\n    return jsonify(health_payload())\r\n\r\n\r\n@app.route(\"/api/v1/corners\", methods=[\"POST\"])\r\ndef corners():\r\n    payload = request.get_json(silent=True) or {}\r\n    if not payload.get(\"imageUrl\") and not payload.get(\"image\"):\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"missing image\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    img = decode_image(payload)\r\n    if img is None:\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"invalid image\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        return jsonify(suggest_corners(img))\r\n    except Exception as exc:\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"corners failed: {exc}\"}), 500\r\n\r\n\r\n@app.route(\"/api/v1/detect\", methods=[\"POST\"])\r\ndef detect():\r\n    payload = request.get_json(silent=True) or {}\r\n    board_size = int(payload.get(\"boardSize\") or 19)\r\n\r\n    if board_size not in (9, 13, 19):\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"unsupported boardSize\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    if not payload.get(\"imageUrl\") and not payload.get(\"image\"):\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"missing image\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    img = decode_image(payload)\r\n    if img is None:\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"invalid image\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    corners = payload.get(\"corners\")\r\n    with_preview = bool(payload.get(\"withPreview\"))\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        result = detect_board_baduk(\r\n            img,\r\n            board_size,\r\n            corners=corners,\r\n            with_preview=with_preview,\r\n        )\r\n    except Exception as exc:\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"detect failed: {exc}\"}), 500\r\n\r\n    return jsonify(result)\r\n\r\n\r\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\r\n    app.run(host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=80)\r\n=== detect service files ===\n\r\n=== check miniprogram services for API calls ===\nName              Length\r\n----              ------\r\n.gitignore            42\r\napp.py              2268\r\nbaduk_detect.py     3437\r\nboard_geometry.py  14341\r\ncircle_detect.py    3621\r\ncnn_classifier.py   3012\r\ndetector.py          245\r\nDockerfile           693\r\nimage_decode.py      833\r\nkaya_corners.py     3481\r\nkaya_stones.py      5669\r\nmoku_detect.py      9915\r\npatch_classify.py   2387\r\nREADME.md           1601\r\nrequirements.txt     130\r\nstone_fusion.py     3562\r\nwatchgo_detect.py   7131\r\nalphago.js          1595\r\nauth.js             2329\r\nboard.js            5276\r\ndetect.js           5633\r\nimage-compress.js   1028\r\nimport-sgf.js       1853\r\nproblem-bank.js     6158\r\nproblem-stats.js     405\r\nsettings.js         2498\r\nsgf.js              6840\r\nshare.js             890\r\nsound.js            3040\r\nstorage.js          1480\r\nthumbnail.js        5447"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":260,"aggregated":"from flask import Flask, jsonify, request\r\n\r\nfrom baduk_detect import detect_board_baduk, suggest_corners\r\nfrom image_decode import decode_image\r\nfrom moku_detect import is_ready as moku_ready\r\n\r\napp = Flask(__name__)\r\nVERSION = \"5.0.0\"\r\n\r\n\r\ndef health_payload():\r\n    return {\r\n        \"ok\": True,\r\n        \"service\": \"weiqi-detect\",\r\n        \"version\": VERSION,\r\n        \"detector\": \"baduk\",\r\n        \"mokuReady\": moku_ready(),\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n@app.route(\"/\", methods=[\"GET\", \"POST\"])\r\ndef root():\r\n    return jsonify(health_payload())\r\n\r\n\r\n@app.route(\"/health\", methods=[\"GET\", \"POST\"])\r\n@app.route(\"/health/\", methods=[\"GET\", \"POST\"])\r\ndef health():\r\n    return jsonify(health_payload())\r\n\r\n\r\n@app.route(\"/api/v1/corners\", methods=[\"POST\"])\r\ndef corners():\r\n    payload = request.get_json(silent=True) or {}\r\n    if not payload.get(\"imageUrl\") and not payload.get(\"image\"):\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"missing image\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    img = decode_image(payload)\r\n    if img is None:\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"invalid image\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        return jsonify(suggest_corners(img))\r\n    except Exception as exc:\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"corners failed: {exc}\"}), 500\r\n\r\n\r\n@app.route(\"/api/v1/detect\", methods=[\"POST\"])\r\ndef detect():\r\n    payload = request.get_json(silent=True) or {}\r\n    board_size = int(payload.get(\"boardSize\") or 19)\r\n\r\n    if board_size not in (9, 13, 19):\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"unsupported boardSize\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    if not payload.get(\"imageUrl\") and not payload.get(\"image\"):\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"missing image\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    img = decode_image(payload)\r\n    if img is None:\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"invalid image\"}), 400\r\n\r\n    corners = payload.get(\"corners\")\r\n    with_preview = bool(payload.get(\"withPreview\"))\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        result = detect_board_baduk(\r\n            img,\r\n            board_size,\r\n            corners=corners,\r\n            with_preview=with_preview,\r\n        )\r\n    except Exception as exc:\r\n        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"detect failed: {exc}\"}), 500\r\n\r\n    return jsonify(result)\r\n\r\n\r\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\r\n    app.run(host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=80)\r\n=== detect service files ===\n\r\n=== check miniprogram services for API calls ===\nName              Length\r\n----              ------\r\n.gitignore            42\r\napp.py              2268\r\nbaduk_detect.py     3437\r\nboard_geometry.py  14341\r\ncircle_detect.py    3621\r\ncnn_classifier.py   3012\r\ndetector.py          245\r\nDockerfile           693\r\nimage_decode.py      833\r\nkaya_corners.py     3481\r\nkaya_stones.py      5669\r\nmoku_detect.py      9915\r\npatch_classify.py   2387\r\nREADME.md           1601\r\nrequirements.txt     130\r\nstone_fusion.py     3562\r\nwatchgo_detect.py   7131\r\nalphago.js          1595\r\nauth.js             2329\r\nboard.js            5276\r\ndetect.js           5633\r\nimage-compress.js   1028\r\nimport-sgf.js       1853\r\nproblem-bank.js     6158\r\nproblem-stats.js     405\r\nsettings.js         2498\r\nsgf.js              6840\r\nshare.js             890\r\nsound.js            3040\r\nstorage.js          1480\r\nthumbnail.js        5447","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781093182537}}
{"type":"message","id":"38a76f36","parentId":"14a9fb98","timestamp":"2026-06-10T12:06:25.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cloudrun weiqi-detect service is the user's own board detection API, not 涨棋网. Let me look at the detect.js service to see how the mini program calls the detection API.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_588jw00BgpyFrg0mIGvM7572","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\miniprogram\\services\\detect.js\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1069,"output":138,"cacheRead":221568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":222775,"cost":{"input":0.00014966,"output":0.00003864,"cacheRead":0.006203904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006392203999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781093182540,"responseId":"e2e86379-5b7a-4a74-b4d7-9a1e3bc667b3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"cefb9119","parentId":"38a76f36","timestamp":"2026-06-10T12:06:25.853Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_588jw00BgpyFrg0mIGvM7572","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const CLOUD = require('../config/cloud')\r\nconst { prepareImage } = require('./image-compress')\r\n\r\nconst MAX_BASE64_LEN = 350 * 1024\r\nconst HEALTH_PATHS = ['/health', '/']\r\n\r\nfunction isAvailable() {\r\n  return !!(CLOUD.ENV_ID && wx.cloud && typeof wx.cloud.callContainer === 'function')\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction buildPath(path) {\r\n  const base = (CLOUD.SERVICE_BASE_PATH || '').replace(/\\/$/, '')\r\n  const suffix = path.startsWith('/') ? path : `/${path}`\r\n  if (!base) return suffix\r\n  return `${base}${suffix}`\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction readBase64(path) {\r\n  const fs = wx.getFileSystemManager()\r\n  return fs.readFileSync(path, 'base64')\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction parseResponseData(data) {\r\n  if (!data) return null\r\n  if (typeof data === 'string') {\r\n    try {\r\n      return JSON.parse(data)\r\n    } catch (e) {\r\n      return { raw: data.slice(0, 120) }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  return data\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction uploadToCloud(filePath) {\r\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\r\n    wx.cloud.uploadFile({\r\n      cloudPath: `detect/${Date.now()}-${Math.floor(Math.random() * 10000)}.jpg`,\r\n      filePath,\r\n      success: resolve,\r\n      fail: reject\r\n    })\r\n  })\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction getTempFileURL(fileID) {\r\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\r\n    wx.cloud.getTempFileURL({\r\n      fileList: [fileID],\r\n      success: (res) => {\r\n        const item = res.fileList && res.fileList[0]\r\n        if (item && item.tempFileURL) {\r\n          resolve(item.tempFileURL)\r\n          return\r\n        }\r\n        reject(new Error('鑾峰彇鍥剧墖閾炬帴澶辫触'))\r\n      },\r\n      fail: reject\r\n    })\r\n  })\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function callService(path, method, data, headerExtra) {\r\n  return wx.cloud.callContainer({\r\n    config: { env: CLOUD.ENV_ID },\r\n    path: buildPath(path),\r\n    method,\r\n    header: {\r\n      'X-WX-SERVICE': CLOUD.DETECT_SERVICE,\r\n      ...headerExtra\r\n    },\r\n    data: data || {}\r\n  })\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function buildDetectPayload(compressedPath, boardSize, corners, extra) {\r\n  const payload = { boardSize, ...(extra || {}) }\r\n  if (corners && corners.length === 4) {\r\n    payload.corners = corners\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  if (wx.cloud.uploadFile && wx.cloud.getTempFileURL) {\r\n    try {\r\n      const upload = await uploadToCloud(compressedPath)\r\n      const imageUrl = await getTempFileURL(upload.fileID)\r\n      return { ...payload, imageUrl }\r\n    } catch (e) {\r\n      // fall back to base64 for local debugging\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const image = readBase64(compressedPath)\r\n  if (image.length > MAX_BASE64_LEN) {\r\n    throw new Error('鍥剧墖浠嶈繃澶э紝璇烽噸鏂版媿鎽勬垨鎹竴寮犳洿灏忕殑鐓х墖')\r\n  }\r\n  return { ...payload, image }\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function suggestCorners(imagePath) {\r\n  if (!isAvailable()) return null\r\n  const compressedPath = await prepareImage(imagePath)\r\n  const payload = await buildDetectPayload(compressedPath, 19, null)\r\n  const res = await callService('/api/v1/corners', 'POST', payload, {\r\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json'\r\n  })\r\n  return parseResponseData(res.data)\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function detect(imagePath, boardSize = 19, corners = null, options = {}) {\r\n  if (!isAvailable()) {\r\n    return null\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const compressedPath = await prepareImage(imagePath)\r\n  const payload = await buildDetectPayload(compressedPath, boardSize, corners, {\r\n    withPreview: !!options.withPreview\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const res = await callService('/api/v1/detect', 'POST', payload, {\r\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json'\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const body = parseResponseData(res.data)\r\n  if (!body || !body.ok) {\r\n    const error = (body && body.error) || `璇嗗埆澶辫触 (${res.statusCode || 'unknown'})`\r\n    throw new Error(error)\r\n  }\r\n  return body\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function probeHealthPath(path) {\r\n  const res = await callService(path, 'GET', {}, {})\r\n  const body = parseResponseData(res.data)\r\n  if (body && body.ok) {\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: true,\r\n      service: body.service || CLOUD.DETECT_SERVICE,\r\n      version: body.version,\r\n      detector: body.detector,\r\n      mokuReady: body.mokuReady,\r\n      statusCode: res.statusCode,\r\n      path: buildPath(path),\r\n      method: 'GET'\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  if (res.statusCode && res.statusCode !== 404) {\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: false,\r\n      stage: 'service',\r\n      statusCode: res.statusCode,\r\n      path: buildPath(path),\r\n      method: 'GET',\r\n      message: (body && body.error) || (body && body.raw) || `寮傚父鍝嶅簲 (${res.statusCode})`\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  return {\r\n    ok: false,\r\n    stage: 'service',\r\n    statusCode: 404,\r\n    path: buildPath(path),\r\n    message: `${buildPath(path)} 杩斿洖 404`\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function checkHealth() {\r\n  if (!isAvailable()) {\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: false,\r\n      stage: 'client',\r\n      message: '褰撳墠鍩虹搴撲笉鏀寔浜戞墭绠?API'\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const errors = []\r\n\r\n  try {\r\n    for (let i = 0; i < HEALTH_PATHS.length; i++) {\r\n      const result = await probeHealthPath(HEALTH_PATHS[i])\r\n      if (result.ok) return result\r\n      errors.push(result.message || `${result.path} 澶辫触`)\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: false,\r\n      stage: 'service',\r\n      statusCode: 404,\r\n      message: `鏈嶅姟 ${CLOUD.DETECT_SERVICE} 鏃犲仴搴锋帴鍙ｏ紙宸茶瘯 / 涓?/health锛塦,\r\n      detail: errors.join('锛?)\r\n    }\r\n  } catch (e) {\r\n    const msg = (e && (e.errMsg || e.message)) || '鏃犳硶杩炴帴浜戞墭绠?\r\n    if (/SERVICE_NOT_FOUND|service not found|鏈嶅姟涓嶅瓨鍦?i.test(msg)) {\r\n      return {\r\n        ok: false,\r\n        stage: 'network',\r\n        message: `鏈壘鍒版湇鍔?${CLOUD.DETECT_SERVICE}锛岃鏍稿鎺у埗鍙版湇鍔″悕`\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    if (/invalid env|鐜/i.test(msg)) {\r\n      return {\r\n        ok: false,\r\n        stage: 'network',\r\n        message: '浜戠幆澧?ID 涓嶅尮閰?\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: false,\r\n      stage: 'network',\r\n      message: msg\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  detect,\r\n  suggestCorners,\r\n  checkHealth,\r\n  isAvailable,\r\n  buildPath\r\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":220,"aggregated":"const CLOUD = require('../config/cloud')\r\nconst { prepareImage } = require('./image-compress')\r\n\r\nconst MAX_BASE64_LEN = 350 * 1024\r\nconst HEALTH_PATHS = ['/health', '/']\r\n\r\nfunction isAvailable() {\r\n  return !!(CLOUD.ENV_ID && wx.cloud && typeof wx.cloud.callContainer === 'function')\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction buildPath(path) {\r\n  const base = (CLOUD.SERVICE_BASE_PATH || '').replace(/\\/$/, '')\r\n  const suffix = path.startsWith('/') ? path : `/${path}`\r\n  if (!base) return suffix\r\n  return `${base}${suffix}`\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction readBase64(path) {\r\n  const fs = wx.getFileSystemManager()\r\n  return fs.readFileSync(path, 'base64')\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction parseResponseData(data) {\r\n  if (!data) return null\r\n  if (typeof data === 'string') {\r\n    try {\r\n      return JSON.parse(data)\r\n    } catch (e) {\r\n      return { raw: data.slice(0, 120) }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  return data\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction uploadToCloud(filePath) {\r\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\r\n    wx.cloud.uploadFile({\r\n      cloudPath: `detect/${Date.now()}-${Math.floor(Math.random() * 10000)}.jpg`,\r\n      filePath,\r\n      success: resolve,\r\n      fail: reject\r\n    })\r\n  })\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction getTempFileURL(fileID) {\r\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\r\n    wx.cloud.getTempFileURL({\r\n      fileList: [fileID],\r\n      success: (res) => {\r\n        const item = res.fileList && res.fileList[0]\r\n        if (item && item.tempFileURL) {\r\n          resolve(item.tempFileURL)\r\n          return\r\n        }\r\n        reject(new Error('鑾峰彇鍥剧墖閾炬帴澶辫触'))\r\n      },\r\n      fail: reject\r\n    })\r\n  })\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function callService(path, method, data, headerExtra) {\r\n  return wx.cloud.callContainer({\r\n    config: { env: CLOUD.ENV_ID },\r\n    path: buildPath(path),\r\n    method,\r\n    header: {\r\n      'X-WX-SERVICE': CLOUD.DETECT_SERVICE,\r\n      ...headerExtra\r\n    },\r\n    data: data || {}\r\n  })\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function buildDetectPayload(compressedPath, boardSize, corners, extra) {\r\n  const payload = { boardSize, ...(extra || {}) }\r\n  if (corners && corners.length === 4) {\r\n    payload.corners = corners\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  if (wx.cloud.uploadFile && wx.cloud.getTempFileURL) {\r\n    try {\r\n      const upload = await uploadToCloud(compressedPath)\r\n      const imageUrl = await getTempFileURL(upload.fileID)\r\n      return { ...payload, imageUrl }\r\n    } catch (e) {\r\n      // fall back to base64 for local debugging\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const image = readBase64(compressedPath)\r\n  if (image.length > MAX_BASE64_LEN) {\r\n    throw new Error('鍥剧墖浠嶈繃澶э紝璇烽噸鏂版媿鎽勬垨鎹竴寮犳洿灏忕殑鐓х墖')\r\n  }\r\n  return { ...payload, image }\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function suggestCorners(imagePath) {\r\n  if (!isAvailable()) return null\r\n  const compressedPath = await prepareImage(imagePath)\r\n  const payload = await buildDetectPayload(compressedPath, 19, null)\r\n  const res = await callService('/api/v1/corners', 'POST', payload, {\r\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json'\r\n  })\r\n  return parseResponseData(res.data)\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function detect(imagePath, boardSize = 19, corners = null, options = {}) {\r\n  if (!isAvailable()) {\r\n    return null\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const compressedPath = await prepareImage(imagePath)\r\n  const payload = await buildDetectPayload(compressedPath, boardSize, corners, {\r\n    withPreview: !!options.withPreview\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const res = await callService('/api/v1/detect', 'POST', payload, {\r\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json'\r\n  })\r\n\r\n  const body = parseResponseData(res.data)\r\n  if (!body || !body.ok) {\r\n    const error = (body && body.error) || `璇嗗埆澶辫触 (${res.statusCode || 'unknown'})`\r\n    throw new Error(error)\r\n  }\r\n  return body\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function probeHealthPath(path) {\r\n  const res = await callService(path, 'GET', {}, {})\r\n  const body = parseResponseData(res.data)\r\n  if (body && body.ok) {\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: true,\r\n      service: body.service || CLOUD.DETECT_SERVICE,\r\n      version: body.version,\r\n      detector: body.detector,\r\n      mokuReady: body.mokuReady,\r\n      statusCode: res.statusCode,\r\n      path: buildPath(path),\r\n      method: 'GET'\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  if (res.statusCode && res.statusCode !== 404) {\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: false,\r\n      stage: 'service',\r\n      statusCode: res.statusCode,\r\n      path: buildPath(path),\r\n      method: 'GET',\r\n      message: (body && body.error) || (body && body.raw) || `寮傚父鍝嶅簲 (${res.statusCode})`\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  return {\r\n    ok: false,\r\n    stage: 'service',\r\n    statusCode: 404,\r\n    path: buildPath(path),\r\n    message: `${buildPath(path)} 杩斿洖 404`\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nasync function checkHealth() {\r\n  if (!isAvailable()) {\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: false,\r\n      stage: 'client',\r\n      message: '褰撳墠鍩虹搴撲笉鏀寔浜戞墭绠?API'\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  const errors = []\r\n\r\n  try {\r\n    for (let i = 0; i < HEALTH_PATHS.length; i++) {\r\n      const result = await probeHealthPath(HEALTH_PATHS[i])\r\n      if (result.ok) return result\r\n      errors.push(result.message || `${result.path} 澶辫触`)\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: false,\r\n      stage: 'service',\r\n      statusCode: 404,\r\n      message: `鏈嶅姟 ${CLOUD.DETECT_SERVICE} 鏃犲仴搴锋帴鍙ｏ紙宸茶瘯 / 涓?/health锛塦,\r\n      detail: errors.join('锛?)\r\n    }\r\n  } catch (e) {\r\n    const msg = (e && (e.errMsg || e.message)) || '鏃犳硶杩炴帴浜戞墭绠?\r\n    if (/SERVICE_NOT_FOUND|service not found|鏈嶅姟涓嶅瓨鍦?i.test(msg)) {\r\n      return {\r\n        ok: false,\r\n        stage: 'network',\r\n        message: `鏈壘鍒版湇鍔?${CLOUD.DETECT_SERVICE}锛岃鏍稿鎺у埗鍙版湇鍔″悕`\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    if (/invalid env|鐜/i.test(msg)) {\r\n      return {\r\n        ok: false,\r\n        stage: 'network',\r\n        message: '浜戠幆澧?ID 涓嶅尮閰?\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    return {\r\n      ok: false,\r\n      stage: 'network',\r\n      message: msg\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  detect,\r\n  suggestCorners,\r\n  checkHealth,\r\n  isAvailable,\r\n  buildPath\r\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781093185852}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2f65689","parentId":"cefb9119","timestamp":"2026-06-10T12:06:31.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the detect service uses wx.cloud.callContainer to communicate with the weiqi-detect service. It calls:\n- `POST /api/v1/detect` - Main detect endpoint\n- `POST /api/v1/corners` - Corner detection\n- `GET /health` - Health check\n\nThis is the user's own board detection service deployed on Tencent CloudBase.\n\nNow, the user wants to look at \"涨棋网\" mini program's photo number interface. Since I can't find the 涨棋网 source code locally and web searches are timing out, let me try to explain what I know and ask for the source location.\n\nActually, wait - maybe I can search for 涨棋网 on Baidu or check if there's a known GitHub project. Let me try one more search.\n\nActually, the user might have downloaded the 涨棋网 mini program's wxapkg (decrypted package) somewhere. Let me check the Downloads folder or a common location for wxapkg files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_r9mNH50XOrijbx0vnkvQ3802","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Search for wxapkg or unpacked mini program code\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\" -Depth 2 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | \n    Where-Object { $_.Name -match \"wxapkg|zhangqi|涨棋\" -or $_.Extension -match \"wxapkg\" } | \n    Select-Object FullName, Length, LastWriteTime\n\nWrite-Host \"---\"\n# Search workspace for any references\nSelect-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.cursor\\projects\\empty-window\\weiqi-sgf\\miniprogram\\**\\*.js\" -Pattern \"涨棋|zhangqi|zqw|photo.*num|photo.*count|count.*stone\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object -First 20","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2228,"output":449,"cacheRead":222720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":225397,"cost":{"input":0.00031192000000000004,"output":0.00012572,"cacheRead