{"type":"message","id":"4b35a6e0","parentId":"172c1beb","timestamp":"2026-06-10T13:01:16.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The files seem to be empty or inaccessible. Let me try a different approach.\n\nActually, I think I've been spending too much time trying to decrypt this wxapkg. Let me take a step back and think about practical alternatives:\n\n1. The user wants to find the 涨棋网 mini program's photo number API\n2. I can't decrypt the wxapkg without the appid\n3. Web searches are timing out\n\nInstead of trying to decrypt the package, let me try to:\n1. Search for the appid using available online resources that might return cached data\n2. Or try to intercept the API calls by using a proxy on the user's phone\n3. Or ask the user to provide the appid from the WeChat mini program management backend\n\nBut wait - I just realized I can try to use the WeChat dev tools' own decryption. The WeChat dev tools CLI has an extract command. Let me check if there's a CLI tool available.\n\nActually, let me just be straightforward with the user. The package is encrypted with an unknown appid and I need help to find it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"涨棋网的小程序包是 V1MMWX 加密格式，需要对应的小程序 appid 才能解密。没有 appid 我没法解包。\n\n不过换个思路——你手机上装了涨棋网吧？直接用真机抓包最快：\n\n**方案：手机端抓包（10分钟）**\n1. 手机装 **HttpCanary**（VNet/小黄鸟）或 **PCAPdroid**\n2. 在手机上打开涨棋网小程序\n3. 进入拍照数子功能，拍张棋盘\n4. HttpCanary 会抓到所有 HTTP/HTTPS 请求\n5. 把请求 URL + 响应格式截图发给我\n\n这样直接拿到 API 地址和参数格式，比反编译快多了。要不试试？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":124,"output":393,"cacheRead":248448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":248965,"cost":{"input":0.00001736,"output":0.00011004000000000001,"cacheRead":0.006956543999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007083943999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781096470549,"responseId":"b2c53e22-d826-47a5-a1c2-da317da28564"}}
