{"type":"message","id":"8573a052","parentId":"50e199da","timestamp":"2026-06-10T13:33:14.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Network keeps failing. Let me try a different approach - use curl with a different User-Agent or try a different APK mirror.\n\nActually, let me just try to directly submit the download to the user via a known URL. The most common source for HttpCanary is Google Play or their GitHub releases page.\n\nLet me try a few direct download links:\n1. https://github.com/MegatronKing/HttpCanary/releases/latest\n2. Direct APK from their releases\n\nActually, HttpCanary's GitHub is at MegatronKing/HttpCanary. Let me try that.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_v5MGjkFKjHhHhTwQGj6y1608","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try to download HttpCanary APK from various sources\nWrite-Host \"Trying to download HttpCanary...\"\n\n# Try GitHub releases (MegatronKing/HttpCanary)\n$urls = @(\n    \"https://github.com/MegatronKing/HttpCanary/releases/latest/download/HttpCanary.apk\",\n    \"https://github.com/MegatronKing/HttpCanary/releases/download/v3.3.5/HttpCanary.apk\",\n    \"https://github.com/MegatronKing/HttpCanary/releases/download/v3.3.4/HttpCanary.apk\",\n    \"https://github.com/MegatronKing/Syringes/releases/latest/download/Syringes.apk\",\n    \"https://api.apkshub.com/file/HttpCanary.apk\"\n)\n\n$downloadPath = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\HttpCanary.apk\"\n\nforeach ($url in $urls) {\n    Write-Host \"Trying: $url\"\n    try {\n        Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $url -OutFile $downloadPath -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 30 -ErrorAction Stop\n        if ((Get-Item $downloadPath).Length -gt 100000) {\n            Write-Host \"✅ Downloaded! Size: $((Get-Item $downloadPath).Length) bytes\"\n            Write-Host \"Saved to: $downloadPath\"\n            return\n        }\n    } catch {\n        Write-Host \"   Failed: $($_.Exception.Message)\"\n    }\n}\n\nWrite-Host