{"type":"message","id":"89284b9b","parentId":"ec486f40","timestamp":"2026-06-10T13:35:29.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Baidu returned 000 (not reachable) and APKPure also timed out. The emulator's network is completely blocked for external sites.\n\nThe network situation is:\n- Host: Can't access GitHub (timed out)\n- Emulator: Can't access external sites (connection timed out)\n- Baidu: Not reachable from emulator\n- APK download sites: Not reachable\n\nThis means I can't download the APK. Let me check if there's any other approach:\n1. Maybe the user can download it on their phone directly\n2. Or I can try HTTP instead of HTTPS\n3. Or use a proxy\n\nActually, wait - I have mitmproxy still running from earlier. Maybe the proxy is intercepting traffic. Let me check if the proxy is causing issues.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_nLowqH0SFvZOUCvX8m9x6054","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if the proxy setting is interfering - remove it\n$adb = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Data\\PlaybackEngines\\AndroidPlayer\\SDK\\platform-tools\\adb.exe\"\n\n# Remove proxy from emulator\n& $adb -s 127.0.0.1:7555 shell \"settings put global http_proxy :0\" 2>&1 | Out-Null\n\n# Test connectivity from host directly\nWrite-Host \"=== Host connection test ===\"\ntry {\n    $r = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"http://httpcanary.com\" -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 10\n    Write-Host \"httpcanary.com: $($r.StatusCode)\"\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"httpcanary.com failed: $($_.Exception.Message)\"\n}\n\n# Try downloading via HTTP instead of HTTPS (some firewalls block HTTPS but not HTTP)\n$downloadUrl = \"http://httpcanary.com/download/HttpCanary.apk\"\ntry {\n    Write-Host \"Downloading via HTTP...\"\n    Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $downloadUrl -OutFile \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\HttpCanary.apk\" -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 60\n    $size = (Get-Item \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Downloads\\HttpCanary.apk\").Length\n    if ($size -gt 100000) {\n        Write-Host \"✅ Downloaded! $size bytes\"\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"Downloaded $size bytes - probably not a valid APK\"\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"Download failed: $($_.Exception.Message)\"\n}","timeout":90,"yieldMs":20000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":576,"output":614,"cacheRead":273920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":275110,"cost":{"input":0.00008064,"output":0.00017192000000000002,"cacheRead":0.007669759999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00792232}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781098522626,"responseId":"7daa1773-979a-4f5a-992d-766853051ca0"}}
