{"type":"message","id":"7d81ae6f","parentId":"202c87c4","timestamp":"2026-06-10T13:35:45.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"CoolAPK also returned 404. The package name might be different. Let me check the correct package name.\n\nActually, HttpCanary's package is `com.gallery.d.httpcanary` or `com.gallery.d.http`. Let me also look for it on other sources. \n\nBut at this point, I've been trying many different approaches without success. Let me just be honest with the user and suggest they download it directly on their phone, which is likely the fastest path anyway. They want to use it on their Android phone to capture 涨棋网 traffic.\n\nActually, let me try one more thing - check if the app is available on the emulator's built-in app store (MuMu has one).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"能连上 httpcanary.com 但不是真站（是 Apache 默认页）。GitHub 和所有 APK 镜像都连不上。公司网络限制了外网下载。\n\n最快捷的方式——**你在手机上直接下载**：\n\n1. 手机浏览器打开 [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/MegatronKing/HttpCanary/releases/latest)\n2. 下载 `HttpCanary.apk`\n3. 装好后打开，去抓涨棋网的拍照数子请求\n4. 把抓到的 API URL 和参数发给我就行\n\n或者手机上搜 **\"小黄鸟\"**，华为/小米应用市场或酷安都有。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":549,"output":290,"cacheRead":275968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":276807,"cost":{"input":0.00007686,"output":0.00008120000000000001,"cacheRead":0.007727103999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007885164}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781098539674,"responseId":"8e8443f3-e925-4707-83d2-6b1e22e9daab"}}
